data.name: mainFrm_cboScanModeToolTip
data.value: Alege metoda de scanare: CULOARE - Imaginea va fi scanata in culori, imprimanta va fi corespunzator automat setata CENUSIU - Imaginea va fi scanata in metoda cenusiu. Scan va fi mai rapida. Imprimanta va fi setata automat pe optiunea alb & negru TEXT - Imaginea va fi scanata alb & negru. este cea mai rapida scanare destinata in special documentelor compuse 100% din text. Nerecomandat documentelor care contin imagini.
data.comment: Choose the scanning method: COLOURS - Acquired image will be full-color, printing mode will be set to color automatically GRAYSCALE - Acquired image will be in grayscale. Scan will be faster. Printer automatically set to Black & White TEXT - Acquired image will be black & white. This is the fasted method, useful for text, books and copies
